This is a fork of https://github.com/EmirXK/bad_apple and it is a
recreation of Bad Apple!! using ASCII. The only thing I've taken
from the original project is the FrameData.lz which I used for the
frames.

I thought it would be nice to play Bad Apple!! on my terminal using
Ruby which is one of the languages I know most about. I inverted the
terminal color so it would display inverted (and more accurately to
the original video). I also added some extra data when loading so you
know it is loading properly.